reviewText: Brook on a Funimation dub. I'm so excited to see it. Lol
Can't wait when this movie come out I'm a big time one piece fan I seen these episodes before in Japanese I'm ready for the English dub

Can hardly wait for this! At long last, we'll finally be able to see the Thriller Bark arc, one of the most awesome arcs in One Piece! The wait for One Piece is worth it, though. I love watching all the episodes! I can't get enough One Piece - I want the One Piece for myself! Keep releasing these, Funimation!
Continues the Thriller Bark Arc and I'm loving it so far
